cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper is primarily focused on person re-identification, which is a computer vision task, hence cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of CycleGAN for style transfer, which is a popular deep learning technique, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) the second most likely sub-category. The paper also involves data augmentation, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia), and regularization techniques, which are commonly used in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
